*RightPanel: Geometry 160x$[vp.height]-0+0
*RightPanel: Colorset 10
*RightPanel: Rows $[vp.height]
*RightPanel: Columns 160
*RightPanel: Frame 0
*RightPanel: Padding 0 0
*RightPanel: Font "xft:Noto Sans:size=10:antialias=True"

